//! Independent wire evidence for TS 29.273 RAR/RAA and AAR/AAA.
//!
//! The input fixtures are hand-authored from RFC 6733 framing and TS 29.273
//! sections 7.2.2.4 and 7.2.2.1. They are not generated by the SDK builders.

